{"tid":589982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【九西死因】未盡力拉票？馮檢基反擊：找代罪羔羊只會輸完再輸","createTime":"2018-03-12T08:41:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T08:57:28.000Z","uid":39464,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3aad4cda0ab50c6b08046ff98ac3e4c230a07297","tid":589982,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T08:41:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180312/large/1520842735_a2d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180312%2Flarge%2F1520842735_a2d5.jpg&h=d2e86ce2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n姚松炎在九西敗選，各界分析其「死因」時將矛頭指向民協，稱該黨未有為姚全力拉票。身在台灣應邀出座談會講述香港形勢的民協馮檢基以WhatsApp回覆《蘋果》查詢時大反擊：「找代罪羔羊，只會輸完再輸！」<br />\n<br />\n馮檢基稱，姚松炎在深水埗區獲得的選票，都比2016年譚國僑參選九西龍時多，又指就算是以2015年區議會選舉麗閣區為例，「我輸99票，姚只輸84票」，直指不應把其他民主派失票算在民協身上，強調敗陣首要是檢討，「（否則）找代罪羔羊，只會輸完再輸！」。<br />\n<br />\n他並指，有些報章及人士專門對付馮檢基，指姚松炎流失的選票中，「有啲因為鬧我哋（民協）。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180312/57936668\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180312%2F57936668&d=JpxaRj1s82kYk0V6mTQ660%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=07945f46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180312%2F57936668&h=1352d562\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180312/57936668</a>"},{"pid":"788ce6f1f2e575b502ccac4e9071e8c0c321b9e4","tid":589982,"uid":38671,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T08:44:37.000Z","msg":"屌票<br />\n不要找代罪羔羊<br />\n<br />\n又係咁熟口熟面既劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4fa6688ab9fadd63d503795398ddada22c7c115","tid":589982,"uid":4783,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T08:46:50.000Z","msg":"今次我支持基哥呀<br />\n其實姚教授自己都係咁講，但唔知點解泛民係都要搵人黎鬧，話人地整到九西輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基哥區選個到都輸撚左啦，點撚樣再幫你洗個到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屈得就屈，今次我支持基哥呀"},{"pid":"5dac6e8e4445c2d5aea4e710f7e867732883678d","tid":589982,"uid":42636,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4fa6688ab9fadd63d503795398ddada22c7c115","tid":589982,"uid":4783,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T08:46:50.000Z","msg":"今次我支持基哥呀<br />\n其實姚教授自己都係咁講，但唔知點解泛民係都要搵人黎鬧，話人地整到九西輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基哥區選個到都輸撚左啦，點撚樣再幫你洗個到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屈得就屈，今次我支持基哥呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T08:49:25.000Z","msg":"搞到牙基變左方丈咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c902f99a61b63754f51e07f0e955564e041651","tid":589982,"uid":48670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T08:50:19.000Z","msg":"牙基好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211730d7435e40e2c0edf6d58edb4380682f76e4","tid":589982,"uid":49456,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T08:50:58.000Z","msg":"馮檢基仲醒過班飯民打手"},{"pid":"e015497044f34fac9d5b9478a8f3c819d1030bbf","tid":589982,"uid":142233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T08:51:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌票<br />\n不要找代罪羔羊<br />\n<br />\n又係咁熟口熟面既劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n焦土派"},{"pid":"a309f8668702e34859f98db6a9b307d27c9dc996","tid":589982,"uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"788ce6f1f2e575b502ccac4e9071e8c0c321b9e4","tid":589982,"uid":38671,